# Hyperbolic Inverses

<div class="block">

![](/img/graphs/calculus/hyperbolic-inverses.png)

Paralleling trigonometric inverses are the hyperbolic inverses as follows:

- *Hyperbolic Cosecant:* $$ \text{csch }x = \frac{1}{\sinh{x}}. $$
- *Hyperbolic Secant:* $$ \text{sech }x = \frac{1}{\cosh{x}}. $$
- *Hyperbolic Cotangent:* $$ \coth{x} = \frac{\cosh{x}}{\sinh{x}}. $$

</div>

